chunks.translated_text:
**Third month:** the sixth day, at the hour of *you*;
**Fourth month:** the fourth day, at the hour of *shen*;
**Fifth month:** the first day, at the hour of *wei*;
**Sixth month:** the twenty-seventh day, at the hour of *wu*;
**Seventh month:** the twenty-seventh day, at the hour of *si*;
**Eighth month:** the twenty-second day, at the hour of *chen*;
**Ninth month:** the twentieth day, at the hour of *mao*;
**Tenth month:** the eighteenth day, at the hour of *yin*;
**Eleventh month:** the fifteenth day, at the hour of *chou*;
**Twelfth month:** the twelfth day, at the hour of *zi*.

At these times, when the Eastern Well of Heaven sets, one bathes and summons the various spirits and gods, all of whom come as desired to be employed and assembled. Bathing and summoning on these days ensures divine efficacy without fail. It also brings wealth and nobility, allowing constant communion with the celestial immortals and sages, prolonging life and enhancing longevity—this is the essential Dao of nurturing the spirit with the qi of the Way, the path to enduring life and everlasting vision. Guard this secret and do not transmit it lightly.

Here ends the *Scripture of the Eight Emperors’ Primordial Transformations of the Cavernous Spirit*.

chunks.overlap_context:
Zheng Siyuan, Ge Hong, Gongming, Jingchun, and Bu Xu all attained it. Though I have seen its methods, I cannot record them all here.

The *Writ and Diagram for Summoning Transcendents and Employing Spirits*, the *Secret Incantations and Verified Scriptures*—on the days of bathing in the Eastern Well, spirits are summoned and employed, but without these texts, success is unattainable.

- **First month:** the tenth day, at the hour of *hai*;
- **Second month:** the eighth day, at the hour of *xu*;
